title: Soundgarden - 1990-04-16 - Dusseldorf DE - RIP Chris Cornell
description: I decided to start uploading again here on tpb, but i need your support to continue. Please only download 1 or maximum 2 of my uploads at the same time. Do NOT try to download 5 or 10 or even more of my uploads at the same time! (this is the reason i have quit for a while, there are too many greedy bastards grabbing all my stuff!) Many thanks to all those friends helping me to seed my uploads, i love you! Together we can keep this awesome music archive alive for future generations. ============================================================================= Soundgarden: Video Source: WDR German Rocklife TV broadcast(on 26th November 1995) and MTV TV Broadcast(on 03rd August 1997) I) Philipshalle, Düsseldorf, Germany, 16th April 1990 01) Announcement by Alan Bangs 02) Flower 03) Hands All Over 04) Gun 05) Loud Love 06) Get On The Snake 07) Full On 08) Nothing To Say 09) Beyond The Wheel Length: 42:48min II) MTV Live`N´Loud, MTV Studios, London, England, UK, 20th September 1996 01) Burden In My Hand 02) Spoonman 03) Blow Up The Outside World 04) Mail Man 05) Black Hole Sun Length: 25:10min Personal: Chris Cornell: Vocals, Guitar Kim Thayil: Guitar Ben Shepherd: Bass Matt Cameron: Drums http://imgur.com/nK9BEir http://imgur.com/S4J4tiV
